import React from 'react';
import {HeaderLogo,StyledWrapper,LogoLink,Options,OptionsLink} from './styles'

import {auth} from '../../firebase/firebase.utils'

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <StyledWrapper>
        <LogoLink to="/">
            <HeaderLogo />
        </LogoLink>
        <Options>
            <OptionsLink to="/sklep">
                SKLEP
            </OptionsLink>
            <OptionsLink to="/kontakt">
                KONTAKT
            </OptionsLink>
        </Options>
    </StyledWrapper>
  )
}

export default Header
